                    <span>Indeed, a brilliant rendition of practical information. I am currently working as a chief technical designer in a financial data warehouse project for a fortune 100 company. Chapter 11 (Data Warehousing) unfolded some time-critical points.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">IT'S POORLY ORGANIZED AND DIFFICULT TO FOLLOW; NOT INTRO BK</div>
